General.Name: Tymlez Group Ltd
General.Description: Tymlez Group Limited provides sustainability focused software solutions in Australia and Europe. It offers Tymlez Platform for companies to monitor and report on their carbon neutral initiative, as well as set and achieve environmental, social, and governance (ESG) targets. The company also provides solutions for Trusted Tokenisation and guarantee of origin. Tymlez Group Limited was founded in 2016 and is based in Southport, Australia.
